:0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"成班男人老狗黎m<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0747df27e3ce58e677991b07d1587cfd434dba55","tid":123620,"uid":61100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"我要睇中醫 個個月飲中藥先黎<br />\n大夫話我寒又虛  黎m又痛到暈係街<br />\n每個月個幾日都好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92946d2a0b8c6603292e11dd3bf8d2b5114c2fb9","tid":123620,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我以前有朋友啲經都好唔掂<br />\n半年都唔黎 之後要睇醫生食藥 一黎黎足半年份量<br />\n之後又唔黎 無限loop<br />\n應該係啲荷爾蒙有問題</blockquote><br />\n黎足半年份量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有個friend都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過之後就正常返"},{"pid":"b35615106bb381eb5ec562372c12e542122fed72","tid":123620,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八個月 有無睇醫生？<br />\n黎返個陣有無勁痛</blockquote><br />\n有呀<br />\n佢叫我黎嗰陣去抽血但我太忙冇去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nday 2-3痛到起唔到身"},{"pid":"183f73e91a244fc9f3c2ba3d1cac2b042388c45d","tid":123620,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"我十幾歲啱啱開始嚟M嗰陣都係10個月1次，大概兩三年後先開始穩定<br />\n每1次會痛撚到你死，好似點谷都谷唔出嘢咁，仲要次次都好少好乾，同埋啲色黑過咖啡"},{"pid":"6fe9a8a72262c6e15e21ba30a5d6d5ae00c34743","tid":123620,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你既黃體素同動情素分泌過量</blockquote><br />\n所以要check hormone<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0673b5d829bff9f95f3ab0f9dab6f1484b197b","tid":123620,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"between我係英國絲<br />\n係黎到經